high_descs: Pick up the large pan on the left of the stove.
Bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Bring the pan to the stove.
Put the pan on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the bottom left of the stove.

high_descs: walk over to the kitchen stove
pick up the pan off the bottom left burner on the stove
turn around and bring the pan over to the fridge
put the pan in the fridge to cool, then take it out again
go back to the stove again
put the pan on the bottom left burner again
anns.task_desc: cool a pan that was on the stove

high_descs: Turn right towards the wall and then turn right towards the green bin on the floor.
Pick up the golden bowl on the stove.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge to cool down and take it out.
Turn around and walk towards the stove.
Place the bowl back to the original spot.
anns.task_desc: Cool down a bowl from the stove.
